Package: dipca
Type: Package
Title: Dynamic Inner Principal Component Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Bradley R. Buchsbaum
Maintainer: Bradley R. Buchsbaum <brad.buchsbaum@gmail.com>
Description: Implements Dynamic Inner Principal Component Analysis (DiPCA) for
    multivariate time series analysis. DiPCA extracts latent components that
    follow a Vector AutoRegressive (VAR) model, enabling temporal prediction
    and reconstruction. Integrates with the multivarious package framework for
    consistent preprocessing and projection interfaces.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports:
    Rcpp (>= 1.0.0),
    multivarious,
    stats,
    forecast
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
